Package: codevar
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Generate encoded variable using secret and text
 Codevar is a command-line utility for generating encoded variables
 using secrets and text input. It supports multiple base encoding schemes
 (base64, base85, base91, base122) and includes base encoding utilities.
 .
 The package includes:
  - codevar: Main utility for generating encoded variables
  - base91: Base encoding/decoding utility (base64, base85, base91, base122)

